{"tid":2517311,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"係連登講環保會俾人圍屌？","createTime":"2021-05-05T08:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T15:45:58.000Z","uid":179902,"like":26,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"fb68514ea206e6346b4aee76ef2a682883b11b63","tid":2517311,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:50:12.000Z","msg":"發覺香港人真係好撚唔環保<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2516333\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2516333</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n環保概念點解會有人反對？<br />\n所謂前人種樹，後人乘涼<br />\n環保、可持續發展未必係我地呢代見到成效<br />\n但長遠對地球發展一定係利多於弊<br />\n至少垃圾可以減少，用黎製造即棄物品嘅資源都可以節省<br />\n<br />\n同埋環保少有少做，多有多做<br />\n例如買外賣自備餐具/餐盒、飲品用少支即棄飲管、用少個膠袋/膠袋再用<br />\n積少成多，其實每人都肯做一件有好大分別<br />\n<br />\n當然有部份環保人士好激進，乜都要管，但呢種人去到邊都係咁黑人爭，所以唔應該因為佢地而反對環保<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"6510a1703fcbe1ca424382d81cdf20643956ef5c","tid":2517311,"uid":281784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:53:12.000Z","msg":"agree <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a16a60e536d814002c3697e6b7171e1f7ff4cd","tid":2517311,"uid":162268,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSaLm1o2UZN2xACwrv785a5fjQ3JUYrka2vHASHZw9htk?filename=g8KAwWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8KAwWr.jpg&h=5b305e11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91dd3f8d560f55f28f3799c58e4d8ac9d1bf0c6e","tid":2517311,"uid":18479,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"個原意係好 但環保撚d行為真係拆自己招牌"},{"pid":"5947ea9163a4b227e74bf8a85340ada2579541ac","tid":2517311,"uid":179902,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"91dd3f8d560f55f28f3799c58e4d8ac9d1bf0c6e","tid":2517311,"uid":18479,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:03:35.000Z","msg":"個原意係好 但環保撚d行為真係拆自己招牌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:16:12.000Z","ms